99
00:06:04,990 --> 00:06:05,824
I won't do that.

100
00:06:07,076 --> 00:06:07,910
I won't.

101
00:06:10,496 --> 00:06:11,747
Because I know what it's like

102
00:06:12,206 --> 00:06:14,041
