Come with us.

125
00:09:21,728 --> 00:09:22,896
We can be a family.

126
00:09:27,985 --> 00:09:29,861
[Mary] Karen, can you hear me?

127
00:09:31,655 --> 00:09:32,531
[sighs]

128
00:09:33,115 --> 00:09:34,241
Karen, wake up.

129
00:09:35,492 --> 00:09:36,660
He's here.

130
00:09:36,952 --> 00:09:38,287
