I'm gonna do?

169
00:15:10,744 --> 00:15:12,162
I'm a hair stylist.

170
00:15:12,704 --> 00:15:13,830
[chuckles]

171
00:15:14,623 --> 00:15:15,457
I...

172
00:15:15,999 --> 00:15:19,711
