way forward.

255
00:19:26,332 --> 00:19:27,292
What you do,

256
00:19:28,042 --> 00:19:28,918
your work,

257
00:19:30,545 --> 00:19:33,840
it's about compassion.

258
00:19:38,928 --> 00:19:40,179
Tell the truth, Mary.

259
00:19:42,473 --> 00:19:43,808
Tell the truth.

260
